name: dotenv-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for environment variable management with python-dotenv
globs: **/*.py
---

- Store sensitive information in .env file and add it to .gitignore
- Use descriptive variable names for clarity
- Load environment variables at the start of your application
- Validate required environment variables during startup
- Use default values for optional environment variables
- Never overwrite .env file without explicit permission
